                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub25_answer" value="1" id="q15251:4_sub25_answer1" /><label for="q15251:4_sub25_answer1">New filing system.</label></div>
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub25_answer" value="2" id="q15251:4_sub25_answer2" /><label for="q15251:4_sub25_answer2">Many changes in a rival company.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub25_answer" value="3" id="q15251:4_sub25_answer3" /><label for="q15251:4_sub25_answer3">New manager of the filing department.</label></div>
                    </div>
                    <p></p><h5>66. What does the woman say about the new change?</h5>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub26_answer" value="0" id="q15251:4_sub26_answer0" /><label for="q15251:4_sub26_answer0">It should have been installed sooner.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub26_answer" value="1" id="q15251:4_sub26_answer1" /><label for="q15251:4_sub26_answer1">It is the manager's mistake to install it.</label></div>
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub26_answer" value="2" id="q15251:4_sub26_answer2" /><label for="q15251:4_sub26_answer2">She liked the old filing system.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub26_answer" value="3" id="q15251:4_sub26_answer3" /><label for="q15251:4_sub26_answer3">She wants to transfer her files herself.</label></div>
                    </div>
                    <p></p><h5>67. What is the weak point for having the new system?</h5>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub27_answer" value="0" id="q15251:4_sub27_answer0" /><label for="q15251:4_sub27_answer0">It will be harder to access the files.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub27_answer" value="1" id="q15251:4_sub27_answer1" /><label for="q15251:4_sub27_answer1">It will take longer to find files.</label></div>
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub27_answer" value="2" id="q15251:4_sub27_answer2" /><label for="q15251:4_sub27_answer2">It will be more complicated to update files.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub27_answer" value="3" id="q15251:4_sub27_answer3" /><label for="q15251:4_sub27_answer3">It will be more expensive for the company.</label></div>
                    </div>
                    <hr />
                    <p></p><h5>68. Where most likely does Mr. Wang work?</h5>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub28_answer" value="0" id="q15251:4_sub28_answer0" /><label for="q15251:4_sub28_answer0">At a safety inspection office.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub28_answer" value="1" id="q15251:4_sub28_answer1" /><label for="q15251:4_sub28_answer1">In the company.</label></div>
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub28_answer" value="2" id="q15251:4_sub28_answer2" /><label for="q15251:4_sub28_answer2">At a safety campaign office.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub28_answer" value="3" id="q15251:4_sub28_answer3" /><label for="q15251:4_sub28_answer3">At a legal office.</label></div>
                    </div>
                    <p></p><h5>69. What is happening next week?</h5>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub29_answer" value="0" id="q15251:4_sub29_answer0" /><label for="q15251:4_sub29_answer0">The factory will be having a tour.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub29_answer" value="1" id="q15251:4_sub29_answer1" /><label for="q15251:4_sub29_answer1">The factory's safety practices will be inspected.</label></div>
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub29_answer" value="2" id="q15251:4_sub29_answer2" /><label for="q15251:4_sub29_answer2">The factory will be renovated.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub29_answer" value="3" id="q15251:4_sub29_answer3" /><label for="q15251:4_sub29_answer3">The factory will receive new machines.</label></div>
                    </div>
                    <p></p><h5>70. What did the woman hope for?</h5>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub30_answer" value="0" id="q15251:4_sub30_answer0" /><label for="q15251:4_sub30_answer0">A day of no work.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub30_answer" value="1" id="q15251:4_sub30_answer1" /><label for="q15251:4_sub30_answer1">Renovation of the factory.</label></div>
                        <div class="r0"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub30_answer" value="2" id="q15251:4_sub30_answer2" /><label for="q15251:4_sub30_answer2">Cleaning of the whole factory.</label></div>
                        <div class="r1"><input type="radio" name="q15251:4_sub30_answer" value="3" id="q15251:4_sub30_answer3" /><label for="q15251:4_sub30_answer3">Increase in their salary.</label></div>
                    </div>
